item.description: Blue Coral Services, an Apple Consultants Network member is based in Las Vegas, NV. The owner, Robert Walden, is a 20 year Apple consultant to the Las Vegas community. He specializes in small business environments, including transitions from a Windows experience to the Macintosh and Apple centric worlds.
